<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to PrintHub Pro</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #4caf50;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Welcome to PrintHub Pro!</h1>
      <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>
        We are excited to have you as a part of our community. At PrintHub Pro,
        we are committed to providing you with the best printing solutions and
        services to meet all your needs.
      </p>
      <p>Here are some of the things you can do as a member of PrintHub Pro:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Explore a wide range of printing products and services.</li>
        <li>Customize your products to match your unique requirements.</li>
        <li>
          Take advantage of our fast shipping and excellent customer service.
        </li>
        <li>Track your orders and manage your account easily.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our
        support team
      </p>
      <p>
        Thank you for choosing PrintHub Pro. We look forward to serving you and
        helping you achieve your printing goals.
      </p>
      <p>Best Regards,<br />The PrintHub Pro Team</p>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> PrintHub Pro. All rights
          reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
